headline: General Mills (GIS) Beats Q3 Earnings Estimates
summary: General Mills (GIS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 5.26% and 2.28%, respectively, for the quarter ended February 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
